propositions.text: The document is titled "重生之千金庶女".
It is part of a series titled "（古代重生）重生之千金庶女---七星盟主".

Someone repeatedly addresses another as "小姐！".
Someone asks if the addressed person is feeling unwell and offers to examine them.
Someone declares, "小女子，你就是我的小女子！".
Someone states they only want to make the addressed person comfortable.
Someone observes a slight blush on the addressed person's face.
A website "www.chnxp.com.cn" is mentioned with the context "笔趣阁 - 免费小说".
The title "《重生之千金庶女》" is repeated.
